    dc:description "Figure 4. Aploparaksis rissae Schiller, 1951, a type from Rissa tridactyla, Alaska: (A) scolex, (B) hooks, (C) hermaphroditic proglottis, (D) cirrus. Scale bars: 100 mm (A, C), 50 mm, (D) 20 mm (B)." ;
